---
title: Conversational Lifecycle Engagement Platform | NHANCE NOW
"description": "Turn on sided engagements and messaging into meaningful and contextual conversational interactions."
---
extends layouts/_layout
block content
  .solution.engage
    .intro
      .container.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1s")
        strong Engage
        h2 Your best customer is your returning customer
        p Achieve high customer loyalty with data-driven contextual and personalized campaigns
    .container.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
      .intro__text
        p Having a deep understanding of customer needs; and engaging with them at key stages of their journey helps improve the quality and outcomes of interactions. 
          strong NHANCE NOW 
          | provides advanced machine learning to help you gather rich customer insights. It also provides a slew of tools – feedback, push notifications, offers, smart notifications - to engage with them throughout their lifecycle.

    .solution__features
      .container
        h2 Features
        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-lg-5.offset-lg-1.col-12.order-md-first.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/solution/engage/engage__img-1.jpg", alt="")
          .col-md-6.col-lg-6.col-12.order-first.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Push notifications
              p Send alerts, updates, messages, greetings, information on new launches, payment alerts, product updates. Use a variety of demographical segmentation to reach the right audience to make the maximum impact. Our detailed visual charts help you to measure the performance of each campaign.
        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-lg-6.offset-lg-1.col-12.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Feedback management
              p Listening to the voice of the consumer as they traverse through your product and/or services journey is critical, to improvise your customer experience delivery. With NHANCE NOW’s feedback gathering tool you can easily capture your customer’s sentiments, run surveys and measure brand experience.
              p Choose from either a 1-5 star rating interface or ask multiple questions with multiple answers. Performance of each feedback campaign can be measured and analysed with a summary list or detailed graphical view.
          .col-md-6.col-lg-5.col-12.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/solution/engage/engage__img-2.jpg", alt="")
        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-lg-5.offset-lg-1.col-12.order-md-first.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/solution/engage/engage__img-3.jpg", alt="")
          .col-md-6.col-lg-6.col-12.order-first.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Personalization – speak 1-1 to your customers
              p The days of one-size-fits-all are bygone. NHANCE NOW’s data engine allows you to configure customer interactions with precision. With 360° customer information you can tailor interactions to add depth, context and meaning.
              p Address customers by their name, greet them on important occasions, send them marketing information which is relevant to them, make smart recommendations and provide customised offers.
